summary: Adds a new location and home for the player
descriptionHtml:
Adds a new location and home for the player
Fast Travel to location is possible
Mist Grove Sanctuary can be found East of Bloated Mans Grotto, in a small rock alcove.

Inside you will find a path leading over a stream and into a small clearing. This is your new home!

Includes:
Tent with chest
Bedroll
Fireplace
Chair
Cooking Spit
Alchemy Table and Enchanters Table both with chest
Blacksmith Forge with chest

ALL CHESTS ARE SAFE

Note: followers will not follow you into Mist Grove. It has no navigation paths for NPC\'s
author: Haonyth
